ns from the Gohana Assembly Constituency on Friday (August 30, 2024).\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Tehreek-e-Insaf\", \"score\": 0.9980096899633835, \"rank\": 0.001994279270667255, \"text\": \"PTI\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Tehreek-e-Insaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Tehreek-e-Insaf\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.738050353815799e-36, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yogeshwar Dutt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\"}, {\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.0111653469885263e-12, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"score\": 0.9053647476904498, \"rank\": 0.10433956012328677, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\"}, {\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gohana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\"}, {\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"score\": 0.9053647476904498, \"rank\": 0.10433956012328677, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have expressed my wish to contest elections to the Chief Minister and the central leadership.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a sportsperson, and an Olympic medallist, and I have contested elections from BJP earlier also, so I want to get a chance\\\", said Mr. Dutt while speaking to journalists.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.738050353815799e-36, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He further added that he wants to contest from the Gohana assembly constituency and he has told the same to the leadership.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gohana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now it is the time for elections, so I want to get a chance to contest from Gohana.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gohana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gohana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not be certain about the future, but I have expressed my willingness, and I have told the leadership that I want to contest.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", he added.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yogeshwar Dutt, who won an Olympic Medal in the 2012 Olympics was defeated by Congress nominee Indu Raj Narwal in a by-poll for the Assembly seat of Baroda in 2020.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1715, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yogeshwar Dutt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yogeshwar_Dutt\"}, {\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2234111621831608e-36, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raj_Thackeray\", \"score\": 0.9998356051284188, \"rank\": 0.000164410183785458, \"text\": \"Raj\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raj_Thackeray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raj_Thackeray\"}, {\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"score\": 0.9053647476904498, \"rank\": 0.10433956012328677, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\"}, {\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vadodara\", \"score\": 0.99